title: Becoming me
creator_credit: Tyson Cunningham, ACMI Digital Storytelling and ACMI
brief_description: When Tyson Cunningham can’t express himself, music does it for him. Although he has long given up dreams of fronting a band like his brother, music is still everything to him, and expresses his emotional life like nothing else.
